        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 13. SEM images. Micanitropis seisia A head, anterior view B tubercles on hemelytron C labial segment I D apical part of labial segment II E head and pronotum, dorsal view F cuneus and membrane cell G trichobothria on middle femur H trichobothria on hind femur I head and pronotum, lateral view J pleura K antennal segments I, II L pretarsus, ventral view M scutellum, clavus and corium N legs O hind tarsus P pretarsus, dorsal view." , "Figure 2. Habitus of Callitropisca florentine, Laetifulvius morganensis, and Micanitropis seisia." , "Figure 4. Male genitalia. Dariella rubrocuneata A aedeagus, dorsal view B aedeagus, left lateral view C genital capsule, dorsal view D left paramere, dorsal view E left paramere, posterior view F right paramere, dorsal view G right paramere, posterior view." , "Figure 14. Male genitalia. Micanitropis seisia A aedeagus, left lateral view B aedeagus, dorsal view C theca D genital capsule E left paramere, dorsal view F left paramere, posterior view G right paramere, posterior view H right paramere, dorsal view." , "Figure 15. Distribution maps A Dariella rubrocuneata, Callitropisca florentine B Labriella fusca, Laetifulvius morganensis, Micanitropis seisia." , "Figure 10. Female genitalia. Callitropisca florentine A dorsal wall C ventral wall of bursa copulatrix E posterior wall of bursa copulatrix. Micanitropis seisia B dorsal wall D ventral wall of bursa copulatrix." ;
